  Locus:
    Page: 224
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Happiness
---
Happiness is manna; it is to be gathered in grains, and enjoyed every day.
It will not keep; it cannot be accumulated; nor have we got to go out of
ourselves or into remote places to gather it, since it has rained down from
Heaven, at our very door.
